    {"id":"UI-REVIEW-001","area":"vscode-ui","title":"Redesign Review Mode into a clear, efficient and accessible end-to-end review workspace","status":"todo","note":"Audit the current Review Mode and add a focused header with review scope and progress, visible current-item context, Previous/Next controls, resolve/reopen and review-decision actions, filters and completion summary. Improve hierarchy, spacing, responsive layouts, VS Code theme/high-contrast fidelity, keyboard navigation, screen-reader labels and empty/loading/error states. Preserve session state, keep actions synchronized with the canonical annotation store and add visual plus Extension Host regressions for the complete workflow."},
    {"id":"DND-EXT-006","area":"drag-drop","title":"Start a literal mouse drag from decoration after-content, CodeLens, Comments threads or Inlay Hints","status":"blocked","blocker":"The stable Microsoft VS Code API exposes commands on these editor projections but no pointer/dragstart source event. TreeView remains the only native extension-owned drag source; clickable pickup/drop is the native editor equivalent."},
